# An entity in the [[Marvel Comics]]
# A [[web browser]] (firebird)
# A [[missile]]
# A [[TV show]]
# A [[software tool]]
# An [[engine]]
# Two [[United States Navy]] [[ships]]
# The first [[steamboat]] to sail the open ocean
# A nickname sometimes used for [[Japan]] after [[World War II|WWII]]
# A place in [[Illinois]] in the [[United States]].
# A place in [[Maryland]] in the [[United States]].
# A place in [[New York State]] in the [[United States]].
# A place in [[Oregon]] in the [[United States]].

